      <title>linux桌面系统ubuntu 9.10常见问题-使用体验</title>
      <link>http://:1313/tmp/2009/12/linux%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9Fubuntu-9.10%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C/</link>
